Implementation Roadmap

A step-by-step guide to implementing StorySell from foundation to execution.

## Phase 1: Identity

Define Founder Identity

Build the Origin Story

Clarify Purpose & Vision

Identify Emotional DNA

## Phase 2: Narrative Architecture

Write the Core Narrative

Build the Messaging Pyramid

Define Emotional Drivers

Write Story Arcs

Establish Voice System

## Phase 3: Story Design

Translate narrative to website & product pages

Build messaging for social channels

Create visual direction based on brand story

Write scripts for brand videos

Rewrite product descriptions

Refresh packaging and onboarding flows

## Phase 4: Growth Loop

Set up messaging experiments

Test visuals vs. narratives

Measure engagement & conversion

Refine story elements quarterly

Align team messaging
